Apple Music係7仔買張卡買十個月送多兩個月，而Spotify加價由$48一個月加到$58一個月 屌<br />\n利申：用開Spotify 貪佢為唔同需要既人整唔同專輯"},{"pid":"5925d0d6086e2d2cb96deec2b14e122a6bc64bda","tid":96344,"uid":20317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"Apple Music 新手不問，點解我聽唔哂成隻碟既？隻碟明明有二十首歌，但我只可以聽到十首<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/02/003918_65623ca45fc502b92debe84092935ef0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F02%2F003918_65623ca45fc502b92debe84092935ef0.jpg&h=b7e33934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就好似呢隻碟明明有22 首歌，但點解我只可以聽到11 首？"},{"pid":"4f7d8bf5e109aa654b0b12d1f1ee5b3b738f4b84","tid":96344,"uid":28387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Spotify 多冷門歌，但係apple music 個player好用好多，都係因為咁先轉用apple music</blockquote><br />\n想試下轉用apple Music <br />\n有啲歌手Spotify 冇歌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSpotify好多日本歌手都無<br />\n想聽coldrain 同 my first story根本就無<br />\n動畫歌更加搵唔到想要個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係最近one ok rock 有新碟先加左好多歌入去<br />\n<br />\n而就算咁樣都唔會轉用apple music<br />\n因為個體驗都幾差下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前買左家庭裝淨係得我一個聽到用到<br />\n其他家人用唔到<br />\n比藍精靈睇發生咩事<br />\n無人識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且音樂介面太唔user friendly<br />\n就好似隨機播放le樣野<br />\n真係比spotify屌打"}]}